(15050, 'Bellyroc cream 50 gm', 'بيليروك كريم 50 جرام', '45', '49', 'Zinc oxide+chamomile extract+olive oil+panthenol+jojoba oil+aloe vera extract+wheat germ oil+avocado', 'Italian cosmetics company > amazon pharm', 'Cream', 'كريم', 'مرطب وملطف لالتهاب الجلد', 'Moisturizing topicals', '50 gm', 'Zinc can be used for the treatment and prevention of zinc deficiency/its consequences, including stunted growth and acute diarrhea in children, and slowed wound healing. It is also utilized for boosting the immune system, treating the common cold and recurrent ear infections, as well as preventing lower respiratory tract infections [L2172].', '6224002280022', '', 2275, '2024-09-26', CURRENT_TIMESTAMP),
