(17510, 'Dextrose 25% (misr) i.v. inj. 20 amp.', 'دكستروز 25% مصر محلول وريدي 20 امبول', '', '8', 'Glucose (dextrose)', 'Misr', 'Inj', 'حقن', '', 'Sterile solution', '25%', 'about dextrose dextrorotatory form of monosaccharide(((glucose))) in hypoglycemia and as a sweetner. mechanism of action of dextrose dextrose is used as an intravenous (((iv))) solution used to supply water and calories to the body. it is also used as dil', '', '', 1006, '2022-07-15', CURRENT_TIMESTAMP);
