(537, 'Amilo 5 mg 30 tab.', 'اميلو 5مجم 30 قرص', '42', '54', 'Amlodipine', 'Alfacure pharmaceuticals', 'Tab', 'أقراص', '', 'Antihypertensive.selective calcium channel blocker', '5 mg', 'Amlodipine may be used alone or in combination with other antihypertensive and antianginal agents for the treatment of the following conditions [FDA label]:
